      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>careful what you say about \"stepping away\" though. i dont mean just taking a vacation or a sabbatical. i mean the kind of rest where nothing is expected of me anymore. where i don't have to wake up and face the fact that i've wasted everyone's time and money. it feels like every path forward is just more of the same struggle. it's like there's no way to actually find peace while i'm still here having to deal with it all.",
